Heath v. Patterson, Warden, et al. Benton S. Clark, Jr., and Robert G. Hanson for petitioner. Duke W. Dunbar, Attorney General of Colorado, John P. Moore, Deputy Attorney General, and George E. DeRoos, Assistant Attorney General, for respondents.
